Waar ben je?


294
00:27:26.021 --> 00:27:27.221
Miners...

295
00:27:28.457 --> 00:27:31.370
Eric! Eric!

296
00:27:32.628 --> 00:27:33.936
Is alles goed, jongen?

297
00:27:35.898 --> 00:27:37.434
Shit!
- Eric!


298
00:28:02.391 --> 00:28:04.260
Jacob?

299
00:28:04.360 --> 00:28:07.341
Haal diep adem. 
Ben je er klaar voor?

