00:28:56.045 --> 00:28:58.184
Vittoria belde. 
Ze wil dat we...

306
00:28:59.114 --> 00:29:01.617
Eric is vermoord!

307
00:29:03.385 --> 00:29:04.585
Wat?

308
00:29:04.954 --> 00:29:06.991
Hij is vermoord!

309
00:29:07.823 --> 00:29:09.023
Wie?

310
00:29:09.859 --> 00:29:11.794
Weten ze wie hem vermoordde?

311
00:29:11.894 --> 00:29:14.228
Ja.
